title: Party with Rocky Patel and 365Cigars.com!
itunes:title: Party with Rocky Patel and 365Cigars.com!
description: Today on The Cigar Authority we're smoking the Rocky Patel 1999 Vintage and the RP Fifteenth Anniversary as the man himself, Rocky Patel, stops by to help celebrate his big birthday! Later in the show it's Tony Blake from 365cigars.com to break down his unique rating system and all things Cigar. And Dave Garofalo challenges Mr. Jonathan and Chuck Morrison to a Trivia Contest. It's show for the ages... It's The Cigar Authority!
